唔多半年 個心仍然好痛<br />\n呢排發夢又成日夢到佢<br />\n明明要準備考dse又專心唔到<br />\n返學日日見 根本放唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDse 好緊要嫁巴打， 頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3446075c84769b0456e6ff794df0de3b9204d2","tid":102261,"uid":58005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"過左三個月已好九成，加油呀巴打"},{"pid":"7abe1e1a6b7108e77b7345221673d7ab60c3eb90","tid":102261,"uid":8986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"分左5個幾月<br />\n初頭自我感覺良好 無人煩唔洗再忍佢<br />\n但係依家又成日心掛掛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca0b9dbe9c7eab4f3819af078036aa4de92598b","tid":102261,"uid":71556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:02:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffc37c9ddf3ce1977f148a891776669bed4a0825","tid":102261,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:07:41.000Z","msg":"飲酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c91864bc88efc6779f702741cb950cd67659ee7","tid":102261,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"我都上星期先分&hellip;口講話工作壓力大，承擔唔起愛情同工作，唔想拖住我時間青春，無心再係我到，但可能實際係對我淡左。絕情到我已經心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但要振作啊巴打，我明白分手真係好心痛好難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，番唔到去以前既日子，傷心係可以但要慢慢走出黎，日子總要過，可能下個更好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係呢段時間充實自己，證明比佢睇無左佢自己都無問題，係佢損失<br />\n<br />\n有咩唔開心就上連登呻，我地都係到同你傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油啊"},{"pid":"a6f87eae800762bae8e626bf32fb953d0450d427","tid":102261,"uid":22990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:30:24.000Z","msg":"個心真係好痛，好似比野壓住就黎心臟麻痺，點解要咁..依家每日都好似行屍走肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994e283d6b159540002e1cee73352a4231fbfea3","tid":102261,"uid":76833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"開頭會愈諗愈傷心 會幻想一齊翻 唔理要用幾耐啦 但時間真係會沖淡一切 我就用咗差唔多两年 突然有一日諗起佢 都唔覺得心痛"},{"pid":"3b2a8c30c6f49bb3b29ab2d11072402964208bf8","tid":102261,"uid":33356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:40:49.000Z","msg":"認真，去跑下步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前都以為自己會死 keep住瞓前喊瞓醒喊 行過某啲地方喊 聽歌又喊 心痛到好似俾人狂用刀插咁樣四個月<br />\n但到你遇到下個啱的人 你就會好快無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03260c4b3680a24cbff274c6614b8f820c9cd29","tid":102261,"uid":81159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:47:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n八年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f869f8c8d747a755d2d1f13c61d0d2a3ef0aeb4","tid":102261,"uid":81159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個心真係好痛，好似比野壓住就黎心臟麻痺，點解要咁..依家每日都好似行屍走肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 我現在都係咁，一訓醒個心就好痛，好似發緊夢咁"},{"pid":"268b771f5839952757e7a29163a0fe709da25ec4","tid":102261,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"分左三個月  好左7成   間唔中有點痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f256669a1366fc307ed8879908b66ac23c8d3fd","tid":102261,"ui